<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 columns">
    <label>Choose the information you would like to appear on the reports you provide to your clients</label>
   	<ul class="no-bullet">
   		<li><input id="check_advisor_name" name="advisorName" type="checkbox" {{#if advisorName }}checked{{/if}} value="advisorName"><label for="check_advisor_name">Advisor name</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_company_name" name="companyName" type="checkbox" {{#if companyName }}checked{{/if}} value="companyName"><label for="check_company_name">Company name</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_website" name="website" type="checkbox" {{#if website }}checked{{/if}} value="website"><label for="check_website">Website</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_personal_email" name="advisorEmail" type="checkbox" {{#if advisorEmail }}checked{{/if}} value="advisorEmail"><label for="check_personal_email">Advisor email</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_company_email" name="companyEmail" type="checkbox" {{#if companyEmail }}checked{{/if}} value="companyEmail"><label for="check_company_email">Company email</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_phone_number" name="phoneNumber" type="checkbox" {{#if phoneNumber }}checked{{/if}} value="phoneNumber"><label for="check_phone_number">Phone number</label></li>
   		<li><input id="check_company_address" name="companyAddress" type="checkbox" {{#if companyAddress }}checked{{/if}} value="companyAddress"><label for="check_company_address">Company Address</label></li>
   	</ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row collapse">
  {{#if active}}
    <label for="company-subdomain">Your white label page name <img src="/img/info.png" aria-haspopup="true" class="has-tip tip-bottom info-icon-image" data-tooltip data-options="show_on:medium" title="You cannot change your company subdomain unless you create a new user account."></label>
    <div class="medium-8 small-7 columns">
      <input type="text" id="subdomain" class="general-input subdomain no-spaces" id="company-subdomain" name="subdomain" placeholder="Example: xyzadvisorygroup" value="{{subdomain}}" readonly disabled required />
      <small id="subdomain-error" class="error company-err invisible">Alphanumeric only.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 small-5 columns">
      <span class="postfix general-input subdomain-postfix">.NestEggGuru.com</span>
    </div>
  {{else}}
    <label for="company-subdomain">Choose your white label page name</label>
    <div class="medium-8 small-7 columns">
      <input type="text" id="subdomain" class="general-input subdomain no-spaces" id="company-subdomain" name="subdomain" placeholder="Example: xyzadvisorygroup" value="{{subdomain}}" required />
      <small id="subdomain-error" class="error company-err invisible">Alphanumeric only.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-4 small-5 columns">
      <span class="postfix general-input subdomain-postfix">.NestEggGuru.com</span>
    </div>
  {{/if}}
</div>
<aside class="notes">
  <p>Your white label page name is the web address you may provide to clients to use Nest Egg Guru. You may also incorporate this link to create a client portal to your Nest Egg Guru calculators from your website.</p>
</aside>
<br>
